high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter to your left.
Grab the spatula behind the bread on the counter.
Face the counter drawer to your left.
Place the spatula into the counter drawer.
Turn right to face the counter.
Grab the spatula on the counter.
Turn left to face the counter drawer.
Place the spatula inside the counter drawer next to the other spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place two spatulas in a counter drawer.

high_descs: Turn left and face the counter with the bread in front of you.
Take the spatula from the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the drawer to your right.
Open the drawer to your right, place the spatula inside and close it.
Face the counter on your right.
Turn left and face the drawer to your right.
Open the drawer to your right.
Place the spatula inside the drawer and close it.
Turn to your left and go the cabinet with white top.
Pick up the kitchen spoon from the cabinet top
Turn to your right, turn left, and face the same cabinet
Open a top shelf, and put the spoon in the shelf of the cabinet
Turn around to face the same table
Pick up the second kitchen spoon from the cabinet top
Turn left toward the same shelf of the cabinet
Open the shelf and put the spoon by the side of the first spoon
anns.task_desc: To put two kitchen spoons inside a shelf of the cabinet
